         <ol class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p ">Check that the load is ready to be energized and it is approved
by responsible personnel.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p ">Make sure that the entire system is running in <ph platform="PxW WxW" class="- topic/ph ">normal operation</ph>.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p ">Check that there are no alarms active, except for any alarm
related to that the feeders in the distribution are open.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p ">For each output/distribution: </p>
               <ol class="- topic/ol ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">Close any external output breaker.</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">Close any outgoing feeders, if applicable.</p>
                  </li>
               </ol>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p ">Confirm any alarms by pressing the <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">C key</b> twice.</p>
            </li>
